defaultven person.
defaultLP3 – Opting out 
defaultLearning objective: Children will become aware of how to ‘opt out’
default from particular uses, sharing etc. of their information
default. They will understand that information they provide could be used for a variety of purposes.
defaultLP4 – 
defaultHow to react to unsolicited messages
defaultLearning objective: Children will consider how they should react to unsolicited emails and text messages that request personal information.
defaultLP5 – Rights and Regulations
defaultLearning objective: Children will understand that
default laws and regulations exist to protect us and to give us the right to access appropriate information.
